snippet.title: Best VGM 666 - Doom - E1M1 ~ At Doom's Gate
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1993 - https://youtu.be/T_HfcZMUR4k

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC, 3DO, SNES etc.
Doom (1993)
E1M1 ~ At Doom's Gate
Robert Prince
